Class FNPRGImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FNPRG, Triplet, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class FNPRGImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements FNPRG
    An implementation of the model object 'FNPRG'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Reserved
    • Lc Height
    • Cap MHt
    • Max Asc Ht
    • Max Des Dp
    • Reserved2
    • Retired
    • Reserved3
    • Uscore Wd
    • Uscore Wdf
    • Uscore Pos
